Features

Core Gameplay
Movement using Arrow Keys / WASD
Smooth snake movement with grid-based logic
Pause / Resume / Quit / Restart functionality
Dynamic difficulty levels (Easy / Medium / Hard)
Adjustable grid size
---------------------------------------------------
Food System

Apple → +1 length
Pumpkin Pie → +3 length
Golden Apple → Temporary immunity
---------------------------------------------------
Game Modes

Classic mode available
Wrap Mode (snake reappears on opposite side)
Obstacle Mode (walls/blocks added)
Ghost Mode( snake can pass through itself)
Forever Mode( snake can't die )

---------------------------------------------------
UI / UX

Changeable background themes
Score display:
Current score
Highest score (session-based)
Start, Settings, Game Over modals
---------------------------------------------------
Sound effects:
General
Movement
Eat
Game Over  
---------------------------------------------------
Leaderboard

Persistent score storage via backend
Tracks:
Username
Score
Cause of death
Duration
---------------------------------------------------

Authors
Om Chavan
Ramanshu Padole
---------------------------------------------------

Future Improvements
Multiplayer mode
